The '''Ringmaster''' was a [[Gender/Legends|male]] [[Humanoid/Legends|humanoid]] who possessed a long tail that he used as a whip to perform with. He was the central figure of a [[Unidentified hologram circus/Legends|holographic circus]], seen on [[Lumpawaroo/Legends|Lumpy's]] holographic table in his home on [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]]. The ringmaster performed along with the [[The Great Zorbak|Great Zorbak]], a gymnast, and the [[Reeko Brothers]], a pair of jugglers, and some holographic tumblers. The Ringmaster was petite in stature and had black [[Hair/Legends|hair]]. He played a [[Horn/Legends|horn]]-like [[Music/Legends|instrument]].

